 Fang</a>,<sup>\n1\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Chan%20KH%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18461182" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140326928740912" co-class="co-affbox">Kwok Hung Chan</a>,<sup>\n2\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Seto%20WH%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18461182" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140326928738544" co-class="co-affbox">Wing Hong Seto</a>,<sup>\n3\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Yung%20R%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18461182" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140326938096640" co-class="co-affbox">Raymond Yung</a>,<sup>\n4\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Chiu%20B%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18461182" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140326927976848" co-class="co-affbox">Billy Chiu</a>,<sup>\n5\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Lee%20P%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18461182" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140326945665168" co-class="co-affbox">Paco Lee</a>,<sup>\n6\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Uyeki%20TM%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18461182" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140326936882896" co-class="co-affbox">Timothy M. Uyeki</a>,<sup>\n7\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Houck%20PM%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18461182" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140326943549184" co-class="co-affbox">Peter M. Houck</a>,<sup>\n8\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Peiris%20JS%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18461182" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140326943546816" co-class="co-affbox">J. S. Malik Peiris</a>,<sup>\n2\n</sup> and  <a href="/pubmed/?term=Leung%20GM%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18461182" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140326932728960" co-class="co-affbox">Gabriel M. Leung</a><sup>\n1\n,</sup><sup>\n&#x0002a;\n</sup></div><div style="display:none" class="contrib-group aff-tip"><div id="_co_idm140326937682992"><h3 class="no_margin">Benjamin J. Cowling</h3><p>  <sup>1</sup>  Department of Community Medicine and Schoo